Class CustomGetOperationStartedListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.etouch.taf.tools.tfsclient.event.CustomGetOperationStartedListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.microsoft.tfs.core.clients.versioncontrol.events.OperationStartedListener, java.util.EventListener

    public class CustomGetOperationStartedListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.microsoft.tfs.core.clients.versioncontrol.events.OperationStartedListener
    The listener interface for receiving customGetOperationStarted events. The class that is interested in processing a customGetOperationStarted event implements this interface, and the object created with that class is registered with a component using the component's addCustomGetOperationStartedListener method. When the customGetOperationStarted event occurs, that object's appropriate method is invoked.
